sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Nutzer
    participant WhatsApp as WhatsApp
    participant PaymentGateway as Zahlungsdienstleister
    participant Merchant as Haendler

    User->>WhatsApp: Initiate payment
    WhatsApp->>PaymentGateway: Process payment request
    PaymentGateway-->>WhatsApp: Payment confirmation
    WhatsApp->>Merchant: Notify payment success
    Merchant-->>User: Confirm payment received